    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies the use of H3 and LISP for Geolocation
   services, utilizing geospatial data to mobility use-cases:
   fresh HDMaps, Intelligent Driving, Cruise and Parking assists.
   This is achieved by:
   - EID addressable geospatial abstraction of road-segments.
   - EID Interface for detections and Uploads, a geospatial-context.
   - EID Routing-Sharing hazards, blockages, parking, road-inventory.
   - Compute-First brokerage of geospatial production &lt;&gt; consumption.
   - Predefined EID geospatial mcast channels to subscribed clients.


	 </t>
